by the salary raise recently?

52
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,480
(Jiaxin is pronounced
as "salary raise" in Chinese.)

53
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:04,280
What happened to Jiaxin?

54
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,840
