60
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:18,880
It's urgent.

61
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:19,920
Got it.

62
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:27,720
Mr. Shen,

63
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,840
I need your advice about something else.

64
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,640
I have a friend,

65
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,040
and he wants to divorce.

66
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,640
Now there are more divorce cases
than marriage.

67
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,560
It's a divorce by agreement or by lawsuit?

68
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,440
By agreement.

69
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,720
