No.

73
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,000
It will be easier.

74
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,440
If they don't have any child,

75
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:59,320
they only need to solve the issue
of property division.

76
00:03:59,360 --> 00:03:59,920
What?

77
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:02,040
As a couple, how's their
properties distributed?

78
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,640
Do they have a premarital agreement?

79
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:06,640
It's an agreement or a legal property system?

80
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:08,120
Who wants to divorce first?

81
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,480
The man or the woman?

82
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,920
How about reasons for divorce?
For the marital infidelity?

83
00:04:17,520 --> 00:04:19,640
You can tell me the whole story
about your friend.

84
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:20,520
Okay.

85
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,240
Here's the thing.

86
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,640
My friend, he...

87
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,440
He went on a cruise trip.

88
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:41,440
Oh, God.

89
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,000
Jiaxin,

90
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,680
