91
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,560
Why do you keep vomiting?

92
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:52,080
It's probably because of drinking cold milk.

93
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,480
How come?

94
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,520
You also felt sick this morning.

95
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,240
I know it.

96
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,880
Probably you have stomach problems?

97
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,680
You think too much.

98
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,080
Nothing wrong with my stomach.

99
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:19,160
The woman doesn't know how rich the man is?

100
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:20,920
She knows.

101
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,200
In that case, if she still
doesn't take this chance

102
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,440
to claim for any compensation,

103
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,760
in my opinion,

104
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,720
she is either really simple

105
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:33,320
or too sophisticated.

106
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,880
What she wants is not just money.

107
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:39,480
But it seems her character is good.

108
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:42,680
I think she is not a shrewd woman.

109
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:44,760
Mr. Yi,

110
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,640
it's not that simple.

111
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,160
Speaking of women nowadays,

112
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:51,000
the more innocent they look like,
the more sophisticated they are.

113
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:53,200
They got married and divorced
in a short time.

114
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:55,720
Better to draft an agreement before marriage,

115
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,920
in case that this woman gets some news

116
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,000
and goes back on her words.

117
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,960
Otherwise your friend
is likely to get nothing

118
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,000
from this divorce.

119
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,560
Get nothing?

120
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,080
But your friend is really bad.

121
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,800
He has a girlfriend,

122
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,520
but he still hooks up with other woman.

123
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,600
As a lawyer,

124
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:16,160
I'm very sympathetic to this woman.

125
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:18,840
What?

126
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,920
Both of them drank too much that night.

127
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,560
They didn't know what exactly happened.

128
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:27,320
Although I'm not a divorce lawyer,

129
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,920
I've heard of so many divorce cases.

130
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,960
Someone like your friend

131
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:33,960
is so irresponsible.

132
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:37,200
He can be in the top three

133
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:39,040
in my ranking list of bad men.

134
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,680
He is not that bad.

135
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:44,200
Well,

136
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,760
it was a misunderstanding.

137
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,320
Forget it. You don't know
what exactly happened.

138
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:48,680
Mr. Yi,

139
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,280
listen to me,

140
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,600
you can know about a man

141
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,200
through his manners to women.

142
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,120
You'd better stay away from him.

143
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:59,480
It seems that your friend even
has no courage

144
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,560
to admit his mistakes.

145
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:04,160
He is irresponsible for his girlfriend

146
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,280
