148
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:08,880
You shouldn't make friends with him.

149
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,200
Jiaxin, the boxed meal again?

150
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,800
I cooked it myself.

151
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:28,760
Hello?

152
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,040
Did you see Chen Jiaxin?

153
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:30,840
She is in the office now.

154
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:32,960
Chen Jiaxin.

155
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:45,440
The lunch break was up.

156
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,600
Why are you still having lunch?

157
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,000
