160
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,080
I'm on it now.

161
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:53,840
Hurry up.

162
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:59,040
Haven't I told you to raise up your head?

163
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,320
Chen Jiaxin,

164
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,440
I've told you we'd have
team activity that day, right?

165
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:04,720
