173
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,400
No, no. I didn't mean that.

174
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:22,080
Chen Jiaxin.

175
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:23,960
Excuse me.

176
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,280
Why did you cancel my gym membership?

177
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:29,040
You wanna turn against me after breakup?

178
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,320
Think about it.

179
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,600
Who bought you this laptop?

180
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,920
Who gave you this mobile phone?

181
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:37,200
Your member fee was automatically
deducted from my account.

182
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:40,000
You selected this laptop,

183
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,760
but I paid for it in installments.

184
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,400
I got this mobile phone
because of recharging activity.

185
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:47,760
You've never spent money on me.

186
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,520
You know how to talk back now?

187
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,360
When we were in a love relationship,

188
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:56,000
you didn't dare to take to me like that.

189
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,880
Let go of me.

190
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,480
Who are you?

191
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,560
Who?

192
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,600
I've told you not to show up

193
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,920
in front of me, right?

194
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,200
What are you doing here?

195
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:10,120
It's you. Let go of me.

196
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,080
Let go.

197
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:12,120
Apologize to Chen Jiaxin.

198
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,000
Let go.

199
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,440
Apologize now.

200
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,160
I'm sorry.

201
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,240
I'm sorry.

202
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:26,680
Gu Chi?

203
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,040
Listen up.

204
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,200
If you keep bothering Chen Jiaxin,

205
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:31,840
I won't let you go easily.

206
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,200
It's my fault. I'm sorry.

207
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:35,840
I'll leave now.

208
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:37,360
Move away.

209
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,240
Chen Jiaxin, look what you've done.

210
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,800
Our company is messed up by you.

211
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,000
Jesus.

212
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,440
Mr. Yi, are you okay?

213
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,160
Do you think I'm okay?

214
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,680
It's obviously the fault of troublemakers,

215
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,240
but you're blaming on the innocent one.

216
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:06,120
She asked for leave for a justified reason,

217
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,760
but you're just making trouble on her.

218
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,280
All the employees here would behave

219
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,720
just like you?

220
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,200
Or this company takes
bullying honest employees

221
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,480
as its company culture?

222
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:26,360
It seems that I need to talk to Mr. Shen about it.

223
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,760
Mr. Yi,

224
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:33,520
it's not like that.

225
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:34,480
We actually do everything

226
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,200
according to...

227
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:35,680
Her note for leave.

228
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:38,680
I approve of it.

229
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:41,600
Chen Jiaxin,

230
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:42,360
come with me.

231
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,320
The air ticket to Bahamas.

232
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,040
Thank you.

233
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:09,760
We set out the day after tomorrow.

234
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:11,520
Great.

235
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,480
I hope when we come back from Bahamas,

236
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,720
there won't be any other problems.

237
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:19,080
They got married and divorced
in a short time.

238
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,600
Better to draft an agreement before marriage,

239
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:25,000
in case that this woman gets some news
and goes back on her words.

240
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,960
Otherwise your friend
is likely to get nothing

241
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,000
from this divorce.

242
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:34,480
In regard to this divorce,

243
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:36,040
if you have any idea or condition,

244
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,800
just let me know and we can discuss it.

245
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,280
Okay.

246
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:44,560
Well,

247
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,400
I have one condition.

248
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:49,040
We need to make it clear now.

249
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:51,320
Shen Dao is really good at this.

250
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:52,640
He is right.

251
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:54,560
I shouldn't have taken Chen Jiaxin

252
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:56,080
as a simple girl.

253
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,480
I'm listening.

254
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:00,880
After we get divorced,

255
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:01,800
I want

256
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,640
to treat you a dinner.

257
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:06,160
But you can't help me pay the bill then.

258
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:08,920
Pardon?

259
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,560
I think you've agreed to my condition.

260
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:13,640
That's your condition?

261
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:16,160
Yes.

262
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:19,000
You always help me out of troubles.

263
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:21,520
But I always bother you.

264
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:23,440
So I treat you a dinner

265
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:24,400
as a way

266
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,960
to express my thanks to you.

267
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:31,360
I hope you accept this condition.

268
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,560
Nothing else?

269
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,400
What else?

270
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,160
She is really a simple girl.

271
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:42,120
I shouldn't have misunderstood her.

272
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,920
Hello, excuse me.

273
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:49,760
Thank you.

274
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:51,640
Help yourself.

275
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:54,720
Excuse me,

276
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:58,600
I haven't eaten anything since this morning.

277
00:12:58,800 --> 00:12:59,760
I'm starving now.

278
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,240
So I'll eat first.

279
00:13:16,160 --> 00:13:16,760
Are you okay?

280
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:25,000
I've finally collected the whole series
of Lantian jade artworks

281
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,480
by Zhongshan Long.

282
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:29,760
