00:38:13,960 --> 00:38:15,680
You should thank your grandma.

850
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:19,800
It's hard to get used to
different form of address.

851
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:20,480
What are you saying here?

852
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:21,400
Just do it.

853
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:23,200
Thank you, Grandma.

854
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:24,680
Don't mention it.

855
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:27,800
I give you one more chance,

856
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:30,360
because I don't want his life

857
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:31,720
to be ruined by you.

858
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:34,280
Anyway,

859
00:38:34,520 --> 00:38:35,920
thank you, mom.

860
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:40,360
Zhengren,

861
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:44,080
I'll ask your cousin to get you a job.

862
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:44,600
Okay.

863
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:51,880
As for you,

864
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:55,000
from now on,

865
00:38:55,560 --> 00:38:57,160
you'll be in charge of...

866
00:38:57,200 --> 00:38:58,200
...of money, right?

867
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,680
Great. Thank you for trusting me.

868
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:01,960
No, I mean front yard and back yard.

869
00:39:04,520 --> 00:39:06,000
The water in the pool should
be changed on time.

870
00:39:06,320 --> 00:39:07,640
The fallen leaves should be cleaned.

871
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,320
That's it?

872
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:12,040
No problem. No problem.

873
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:14,640
Mom, I can do anything.

874
00:39:14,680 --> 00:39:16,560
I'll live up to you.

875
00:39:16,600 --> 00:39:17,320
Alright then.

876
00:39:17,360 --> 00:39:18,440
I won't let you down.

877
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:29,960
I'm carrying a baby

878
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:33,040
in my belly now.

879
00:39:37,720 --> 00:39:40,480
I've never expected
I'll be a mother so early.

880
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:45,280
Do I need to tell him?

881
00:39:55,160 --> 00:39:56,440
I can't get you.

882
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:58,800
You'll go abroad again
after your breakup in a cruise trip.

883
00:39:59,200 --> 00:39:59,840
Here are your clothes.

884
00:39:59,880 --> 00:40:00,440
Thank you.

885
00:40:02,060 --> 00:40:02,740
(Wedding Certificate
Wang Xiyi; Chen Jiaxin)

886
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:06,640
What are you doing?

887
00:40:07,120 --> 00:40:07,680
Nothing.

888
00:40:08,040 --> 00:40:08,480
Well,

889
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:11,680
I haven't finished packing yet.

890
00:40:12,040 --> 00:40:13,280
I'm in a hurry.

891
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:14,880
I can help you.

892
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:15,440
No.

893
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:18,520
I still remember what you did last time.

894
00:40:19,040 --> 00:40:20,280
I'll do it myself.

895
00:40:23,120 --> 00:40:24,240
It's for you.

896
00:40:25,220 --> 00:40:26,560
(Hyaluronic Acid Moisturizing Base Solution)

897
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:28,160
It's the base solution

898
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:30,880
I got you during my cruise trip, right?

899
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:33,800
You'll go abroad tomorrow, right?

900
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:35,040
So you should look good tomorrow.

901
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:38,600
Maybe you'll meet your Mr. Right.

902
00:40:40,200 --> 00:40:42,360
What will you use if you give it to me?

903
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,040
I've already bought it.

904
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:47,120
Here you are.

905
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:51,600
You look haggard.

906
00:40:51,840 --> 00:40:52,760
You know what?

907
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:55,160
This base solution is really good.

908
00:40:56,160 --> 00:40:57,400
Have a try now.

909
00:40:57,640 --> 00:40:57,920
Okay.

910
00:40:58,280 --> 00:40:59,000
I need to go to bed now.

911
00:41:11,620 --> 00:41:17,460
(Wedding Certificate
Wang Xiyi; Chen Jiaxin)

912
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:20,760
How should I tell him?

913
00:41:24,980 --> 00:41:29,180
(Wedding Certificate
Wang Xiyi; Chen Jiaxin)

914
00:41:36,500 --> 00:41:38,740
(Anna)

915
00:41:48,120 --> 00:41:48,560
Hello.

916
00:41:49,200 --> 00:41:50,680
What takes you so long to answer it?

917
00:41:51,240 --> 00:41:53,040
Did you forget what day was yesterday?

918
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:54,760
Well.

919
00:41:55,920 --> 00:41:58,480
It was my first day to perform
at the Paris Opera.

920
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:01,080
Right.

921
00:42:02,400 --> 00:42:03,800
Your performance was going well?

922
00:42:04,040 --> 00:42:04,440
Yes.

923
00:42:04,720 --> 00:42:05,360
That was great.

924
00:42:06,120 --> 00:42:08,800
We received a standing ovation
for over ten minutes.

925
00:42:10,520 --> 00:42:12,520
But when I got back to the backstage,

926
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:14,000
I didn't receive your flowers.

927
00:42:16,800 --> 00:42:17,440
I'm sorry.

928
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:19,920
I've been busy recently.

929
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:22,000
Something has been bothering me.

930
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:23,600
I promise

931
00:42:24,160 --> 00:42:25,920
I'll give you the most special gift next time.

932
00:42:26,240 --> 00:42:26,880
Xiyi,

933
00:42:28,120 --> 00:42:29,520
I should feel sorry.

934
00:42:33,240 --> 00:42:35,080
You always support me in every way.

935
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:37,440
But when you're in trouble,

936
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:39,880
I can't be there with you.

937
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:42,800
I feel so sorry.

938
00:42:43,200 --> 00:42:44,080
You don't have to.

939
00:42:44,720 --> 00:42:46,960
Now you're in a crucial stage of your life.

940
00:42:47,800 --> 00:42:49,520
If you can pursue your dream,

941
00:42:50,120 --> 00:42:51,720
I'll be relieved.

942
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:52,240
Okay.

943
00:42:53,520 --> 00:42:55,560
If you didn't forget to send
me flowers this time,

944
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:57,360
I don't even know you mean a lot to me.

945
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:01,640
Xiyi,

946
00:43:02,960 --> 00:43:03,720
I do.

947
00:43:05,600 --> 00:43:06,320
What?

948
00:43:07,280 --> 00:43:08,400
I've already known

949
00:43:08,760 --> 00:43:10,200
you wanted to propose
to me during cruise trip.

950
00:43:11,160 --> 00:43:12,480
When this performance is over,

951
00:43:13,040 --> 00:43:13,960
let's get married then.

952
00:43:14,840 --> 00:43:15,600
I've made up my mind.

953
00:43:16,320 --> 00:43:19,480
I wanna be your bride
rather than a white swan.

954
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:31,440
Anna,

955
00:43:33,080 --> 00:43:34,720
when I get my work done,

956
00:43:36,160 --> 00:43:37,920
I promise I'll give you a perfect wedding.

957
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:39,040
Wait,

958
00:43:39,680 --> 00:43:40,240
don't you think

959
00:43:40,280 --> 00:43:42,560
you owe me a proposal before that?

960
00:43:46,520 --> 00:43:47,280
No problem.

961
00:43:48,840 --> 00:43:50,320
I should go back to sleep now.

962
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:53,760
I missed you so much that
I couldn't sleep last night.

963
00:43:54,360 --> 00:43:57,760
If I can't get more sleep,
I'll be a white swan with black eyes.

964
00:43:59,440 --> 00:44:00,120
Go ahead.

965
00:44:01,360 --> 00:44:02,040
Bye bye.

966
00:44:02,560 --> 00:44:03,240
Bye bye.

967
00:44:12,140 --> 00:44:13,460
(Wedding Certificate
Wang Xiyi; Chen Jiaxin)

968
00:44:19,780 --> 00:44:21,580
♪Those mistakes I made in my life,♪

969
00:44:22,060 --> 00:44:24,780
♪I take them well.♪

970
00:44:26,580 --> 00:44:29,180
♪You don't know a good thing♪

971
00:44:30,060 --> 00:44:32,540
♪till it's gone.♪

972
00:44:33,460 --> 00:44:35,220
♪When you fall in love with someone,♪

973
00:44:35,740 --> 00:44:38,700
♪you start to hope
that love will be everlasting.♪

974
00:44:40,020 --> 00:44:42,820
♪In the great wilderness of the world,
I can only see you.♪

975
00:44:43,460 --> 00:44:47,140
♪I want to give all my love to you.♪

976
00:44:47,180 --> 00:44:48,460
♪Can you summon♪

977
00:44:48,900 --> 00:44:53,100
♪love?♪

978
00:44:53,940 --> 00:44:55,180
♪What would you do♪

979
00:44:55,700 --> 00:44:59,540
♪for love?♪

980
00:44:59,660 --> 00:45:02,780
♪Don't say "I love you" yet.♪

981
00:45:03,100 --> 00:45:07,060
♪Don't fall in love with me yet.♪

982
00:45:07,380 --> 00:45:10,260
♪Fairytale should have
an impressive beginning♪

983
00:45:10,780 --> 00:45:16,260
♪regardless of its ending.♪

984
00:45:16,540 --> 00:45:19,100
♪There is an understanding between us♪

985
00:45:19,180 --> 00:45:22,940
♪that you will finally find me.♪

986
00:45:23,100 --> 00:45:26,220
♪You are the only one
who understands why I keep waiting.♪

987
00:45:26,540 --> 00:45:30,420
♪I will not run away from it,
because you are my destiny.♪

988
00:45:35,820 --> 00:45:37,540
♪I'm looking for you.♪

989
00:45:37,660 --> 00:45:39,180
♪I'm waiting for you.♪

990
00:45:39,260 --> 00:45:43,740
♪I'm deeply in love with you.♪
